{{Infobox Union |name= |country= [[Bangladesh]] |affiliation= [[World Federation of Trade Unions|WFTU]] |members= |full_name= Bangladesh Trade Union Kendra |native_name= |image= |founded= |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Dhaka]], Bangladesh |people= |website= |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''Bangladesh Trade Union Kendra''' ({{lang-bn|বাংলাদেশ ট্রেড ইউনিয়ন কেন্দ্র}} Bānlādēśa ṭrēḍa i'uniẏana kēndra) is a national [[trade union]] federation in [[Bangladesh]]. It is affiliated with the [[World Federation of Trade Unions]].
BTUK is politically tied to the [[Communist Party of Bangladesh]], although the federation has started to become somewhat more independent in recent years.
