The '''N1''' is a national highway of [[Guinea]], It connects the city of [[Conakry]] to [[Nzerekore]] and to the north with [[Kankan]] and eventually by the [[N7 road (Guinea)|N7 road]] and [[N32 road (Guinea)|N32 road]] to the border with [[Mali]]. It also passes through the city of [[Kouroussa]].

